            }

              msg: window.location.host,
              wl_avgv1: fsp,
              wl_avgv2: csr || 0,
              c1: window.__hasSSR__ ? 1 : 0,
            });
          }
        }
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
          if (window.timings) {
            if (window.timings.render) {
              report();
            } else {
              setTimeout(function () {
                report();
              }, 3000);
            }
          }
        })
